///      -> idx 0 (unquoted): " one  " -> groups: [" ", "one", "  "] -> keep non-space: ["one"]
///      -> idx 1 (quoted): " two  " -> keep as: [" two  "]
///      -> idx 2 (unquoted): "three    four" -> groups: ["three", "    ", "four"] -> keep non-space: ["three", "four"]
///      - Now we have: ["one"], [" two  "], ["three", "four"]
