<p>Unfortunately, while <code>rustyline</code> now replaces the preceding whitespace with the &quot;.&quot; stored in the handler struct, it positions the cursor before not after the &quot;.&quot;, so I cannot continue entering the column name unless I move the cursor right first:</p>
<pre class="lang-sql prettyprint-override"><code>zql&gt; SELECT bo&lt;TAB&gt;|
zql&gt; SELECT book |
zql&gt; SELECT book|.
