                // rustyline versions if the movement consumes the text to be replaced.
                //
                // Let's try: Move backward `whitespace_count`, then Replace that movement with the dot.
                // Movement::BackwardChar(n) selects n characters to the left.
                // Cmd::Replace(Movement::BackwardChar(n), Some(".")) will delete those n chars and insert "./".
